{"title":"ly的cr传奇","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-6039","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>ly最喜欢玩cr了。</p><p>他每天除了暗推，陪510，就是在玩cr。</p><p>有一天，他考试考了段1，脑力值降到了0，做不出题目了。</p><p>他的<span style=\"\">inferno dragon初始伤害为1，每秒翻倍。他想知道过</span></p><p><span style=\"\">x秒他的<span style=\"\">inferno dragon的伤害n是多少。</span></span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一行，一个时间x</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一行，伤害值n</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>对于70%的数据，0&lt;x&lt;15</p><p>对于100%的数据，0&lt;x&lt;30</p><p>（不要说我没玩过cr，我要是输入<span style=\"\">inferno dragon的真实数据就没几个人做得出来）</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}